data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.875% interest rate! Call agent for more details.Simply stunning inside and out! Located n a cul-de-sac with a fully fenced yard!  Garden boxes with watering system.  Home boasts an open floor plan.  5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms.  Brand new carpet and paint throughout. Perfect Mother-in-law space in the daylight basement with full walk out.  Newly purchased HVAC, water heater, and appliances.  Home also features a water softener.  Enjoy the beautiful views from your TREX deck.  Conveniently located close to shopping, schools, parks, freeway access and more! Extra large Colonial 50 Liberty safe in basement.  You do not want to miss this home!
